---
title: Thai Red Coconut & Veggie Noodle Soup with Crushed Peanuts & Coriander
description: This fast one-pot noodle soup is a delicious and easy way to switch up your dinner! Green curry paste and udon
noodles are the key players, while a sprinkling of crushed peanuts add flavour and crunch.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
